{"tid":1562863,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求心理學人士入嚟","createTime":"2019-09-12T07:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:23:36.000Z","uid":302271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac8e980ee9acf6d15068395929e551786981639","tid":1562863,"uid":302271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cfccadd2a81d55953b2b86bcd39c03ea68a4ed","tid":1562863,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:44:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfc9a4e9afd4b796e430f9fa7fa7db515571a025","tid":1562863,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:44:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c3b364d025d77e42fdd17148079a02ce9d2555d7","tid":1562863,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882d8133a598ae498c66f92d5ee4eecd26031c98","tid":1562863,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97eb1b5d988ab853706d33fe43cd35d929304a1e","tid":1562863,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"882d8133a598ae498c66f92d5ee4eecd26031c98","tid":1562863,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec892b148c767f0f9beae834425e9e4b0cb06573","tid":1562863,"uid":309873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:20:59.000Z","msg":"建議大家唔好吹奏Zimbardo既路西法效應。成個實驗好唔科學。如果咁都寫到文，我做咩實驗都可以勁significant.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/blog/freedom-learn/201310/why-zimbardo-s-prison-experiment-isn-t-in-my-textbook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psychologytoday.com%2Fus%2Fblog%2Ffreedom-learn%2F201310%2Fwhy-zimbardo-s-prison-experiment-isn-t-in-my-textbook&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=acbdd458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/blog/freedom-learn/201310/why-zimbardo-s-prison-experiment-isn-t-in-my-textbook</a>"},{"pid":"09fc863040a21a5dc3357e576b5d2b809354d2f1","tid":1562863,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:21:15.000Z","msg":"利申：冇讀過犯罪心理學 只係睇過少少一般心理學的書 真係9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得可以用本我 自我 超我黎解釋<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/本我、自我与超我\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E6%9C%AC%E6%88%91%E3%80%81%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8E%E8%B6%85%E6%88%91&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=0dc48972\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/本我、自我与超我</a><br />\n人人都會有原始我慾望 例如飢餓感 性慾等等<br />\n肚餓的時候想食野<br />\n有性慾的時候會想扑野<br />\n但點解我地唔會隨便走入店舖拎野食<br />\n點解我地唔會喺條街隨便捉條女黎強姦？<br />\n因為1.我地知道咁做的話 道德上係錯 所以我地唔應該咁做<br />\n2.因為我地知道咁做係犯法 犯法會受到懲罰 我地唔想受到懲罰 所以我地唔會咁做<br />\n<br />\n1的諗法係出於道德<br />\n呢種諗法係能夠放棄個人利益(冇得發洩性慾)去實踐道德<br />\n又或者換個角度睇<br />\n其實唔係放棄個人利益 而係道德感(或者叫良知良心)比原始慾望(飢餓 性慾)更重要<br />\n實踐道德喺心理上的獲益比原始慾望得到滿足的獲益更多(道德&gt;原始慾望)<br />\n所以我地會壓抑住原始慾望 而唔去偷野食 強姦 從而實踐道德<br />\n<br />\n2的諗法係出於個人利益<br />\n只要我做呢件事的得益多過損失 我就會做<br />\n例如我願意以20年刑期作為代價(損失) 去強姦自己鍾意的女仔(得益)<br />\n我願意以終生監禁作為代價(損失) 去殺死自己討厭的人(得益)<br />\n呢種人係冇道德感 或者只係有極少道德感<br />\n佢地佢將原始慾望置於道德之上(原始慾望&gt;道德)<br />\n呢種人可能知道自己所做的事係錯 但仍然會去做<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下其實仲有第3種人<br />\n就係佢地根本唔覺得強姦人係錯<br />\n前日睇港台9：30套希特拉的幫兇<br />\n講納粹戰犯阿道夫&middot;艾希曼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/hitlersmostwanted\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fhitlersmostwanted&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=a11807c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/hitlersmostwanted</a><br />\n佢係參與處置猶太人的官員<br />\n負責將猶太人送去集中營<br />\n節目臨尾好似話佢仲打算出書講述自己喺納粹時期的威水史<br />\n話佢根本唔覺得自己所做的事係錯 仲以此為榮<br />\n<br />\n答返你條問題<br />\n1. 喺咩情況咩心理下，一班執法嘅公僕會進行輪姦少女嘅行為？<br />\n我自己相信黑警係屬於第二，三種人<br />\n由以前開始 唯一約束住佢地的方法就係法律<br />\n你見到當71前林鄭失蹤2星期後首次露面就接見四大警察工會 <br />\n並承諾唔會成立獨立調查委員會(即係話比佢地知唔洗擔心犯法會比人查)<br />\n呢日開始法律已經約束唔到黑警<br />\n之後黑警的行為就越來越瘋狂<br />\n好似714前林鄭又答應唔會出賣警隊<br />\n之後黑警的行為就更加瘋狂<br />\n之後得到中共開聲支持 就更加更加瘋狂<br />\n<br />\n至於第二條問題<br />\n我覺得紀念的機會唔大<br />\n你覺得佢會唔會以成功強姦幾多個人為榮？<br />\n我覺得唔會"},{"pid":"919ebf5b08fb16c4165b9be578ee6c4eb1bf458f","tid":1562863,"uid":141508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3b364d025d77e42fdd17148079a02ce9d2555d7","tid":1562863,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"唔洗吹奏路西法效應，用史丹福監獄實驗同米爾格倫服從實驗已經解釋到，即使佢個底再靚都好，佢都會陷落而成為政權嘅爪牙，而會反抗既系極少數(服從實驗)，當上下關係完美咁形成，會搵方法去羞辱下位者系必然既事(監獄實驗)，強姦只係其中一個表達方式(強姦通常係為咗展現權力大於真系為咗解決性欲)。"}]}